title: Lavender Haze
description:
The first song to kick off the Midnights album sets up the whole vibe and even starts with something that Taylor has been telling us all along.. Meet me at midnight! But the song title itself caused some controversy right out of the gate! We discuss.
What did we miss? What would you like from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
